            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a>&nbsp;11 月 10 日消息，盛色“N50 Pro 5&nbsp;机械臂版”24.5&nbsp;英寸显示器现已在京东开启首销，这款显示器主打“1080P 200Hz（IT之家注：180Hz&nbsp;超频）”，用户可领取“平台 20 元补贴券”，<strong>到手价 649&nbsp;元</strong>。</p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/ID8wRm9" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/56420/34/28797/89763/66c68fcbFb79a5e28/7fa5acdf679212fc.jpg" title="盛色“N50 Pro 5 机械臂版”24.5 英寸显示器首销：1080P 超频 200Hz，649 元" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name">盛色“N50Pro5”机械臂版显示器</span></span><span class="card-abstract"></span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price"> 649 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1359" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/838918a8-da5d-4ee0-8377-70b2115d582c.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xdy9xdzE0OS5wbmc=,t_100,g_7,y_15,x_15,a_0/format,f_auto" title="盛色“N50 Pro 5 机械臂版”24.5 英寸显示器首销：1080P 超频 200Hz，649 元" width="970" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="830" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/74c9591f-63c7-4305-a000-0a700215af6b.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xdy9xdzE0Ni5wbmc=,t_100,g_7,y_15,x_15,a_0/format,f_auto" title="盛色“N50 Pro 5 机械臂版”24.5 英寸显示器首销：1080P 超频 200Hz，649 元" width="952" /></p><p>据介绍，这款显示器配备&nbsp;1920 x 1080&nbsp;分辨率&nbsp;200Hz（180Hz&nbsp;超频）面板，亮度&nbsp;400&nbsp;尼特，响应速度&nbsp;1ms，静态对比度&nbsp;1000:1，支持&nbsp;8-Bit&nbsp;色彩，覆盖&nbsp;99% sRGB 色域。</p><p>这款显示器配有机械臂支架，支持各种角度随意升降 / 旋转 / 倾斜；提供&nbsp;&nbsp;1&nbsp;个&nbsp;HDMI 2.0&nbsp;接口、1&nbsp;个&nbsp;DP1.4&nbsp;接口、1&nbsp;个音频接口。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="791" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/be609348-6bea-4323-b219-7186e2875aa1.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="盛色“N50 Pro 5 机械臂版”24.5 英寸显示器首销：1080P 超频 200Hz，649 元" width="946" /></p><p>IT之家附显示器参数信息如下：</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1084" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/a290ca17-80f0-41f4-b928-07a5f80c0d6e.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xdy9xdzE0Ni5wbmc=,t_100,g_7,y_15,x_15,a_0/format,f_auto" title="盛色“N50 Pro 5 机械臂版”24.5 英寸显示器首销：1080P 超频 200Hz，649 元" width="946" /></p><p>2024 年 11.11 大促全网好价合集：<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fcontentlist%3Fapi%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fnapi.ithome.com%252Fapi%252Ftopmenu%252Fgetmenufeeds%252F166%252F0%252Fnone%252F0%26title%3D2024%25E5%258F%258C11%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BF%2583%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E9%2580%2589%26mode%3D0" target="_blank" title="点此查看">点此查看</a></p><p><span class="font-color-red"><strong>京东无门槛红包&nbsp;</strong></span>至高 11111 元：<a href="https://u.jd.com/CaQySbH" target="_blank" title="点此抽今日红包"><strong>点此抽今日红包</strong></a></p><p><span class="font-color-orangered"><strong>天猫无门槛红包&nbsp;</strong></span>至高 24888 元：<strong><a href="https://s.click.taobao.com/w26hFPt" target="_blank">点此抽今日红包</a></strong></p><br /><p><br /></p><p class="ad-tips">广告声明：文内含有的对外跳转链接（包括不限于超链接、二维码、口令等形式），用于传递更多信息，节省甄选时间，结果仅供参考，IT之家所有文章均包含本声明。</p>
